snippet.title: Lets Pet Pets  - Early Access  Trailer
snippet.description:
Let's Pet Pets lets you pet pets of all shapes and sizes. Pet tons of pets, get pet points, purchase helping hands, buy upgrades, hatch eggs to get new pets and grow your pet collection with pets of different rarities. Become the number 1 best pet petter in the world! 
Click here now to join the adventure!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2254600/Lets_Pet_Pets/
